SUMMARY:The Olive Oil Experience at Great Bear Vineyards
DESCRIPTION:The Olive Oil Experience Box at Great Bear Vineyards in Davis \nSaturday\, May 2 | 12–5pmTicket Includes: Olive Oil\, Cheese Box & Glass of Wine\nMore than a meal… this is a flavor-filled tasting journey. \nJoin us at the vineyard for a deliciously curated Olive Oil Experience Box\, where our handcrafted olive oil takes center stage—paired with a selection of sweet and savory bites designed to highlight just how magical great olive oil can be.\n Rustic bread for dipping Marin cheese Apricots & fresh strawberries Honey for a touch of sweetness And a perfectly indulgent olive oil cake to finish\nEach box is paired with a glass of wine\, making this the perfect way to relax\, picnic\, and savor the afternoon among the vines.\n Whether you’re a foodie\, a wine lover\, or just looking for a unique vineyard experience\, this is one you won’t want to miss.\n Order in advance to avoid disappointment!\n Wine Club members—don’t forget to log in for your exclusive discount at checkout.\nCome sip\, dip\, and savor with us!
URL:https://visitdavis.org/event/the-olive-oil-experience-at-great-bear-vineyards/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards 24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
