SUMMARY:Mother’s Day Lunch @ Great Bear Vineyards
DESCRIPTION:Mother’s Day Lunch at Great Bear Vineyards in Davis\nSunday\, May 10 | 1:30–3:30pm$40 per person\nTreat Mom to an afternoon she’ll truly savor  Celebrate Mother’s Day with a relaxed\, elegant lunch surrounded by vineyard views\, springtime beauty\, and the people she loves most.\n Begin with a welcome glass of sparkling wine or mimosa (optional)\, then settle in for a generous\, beautifully prepared lunch designed to delight every palate. Enjoy live music by Duet Allegro\, featuring Spanish guitar and classical violin—perfectly setting the mood for a warm\, joyful afternoon.\n Mother’s Day Lunch Menu Includes:\nSeasonal Fresh Fruit Bowl\nCranberry Apple Quinoa Salad\nMediterranean Orzo Pasta Salad\nRoasted Baby Potatoes with Fresh Herbs\nSeasonal Sautéed Vegetables\nItalian Herb Grilled Chicken with Caprese\nFilet of Beef in Madeira Sauce\nSalmon\nVegetarian Zucchini Boats (limited availability—please request when booking)\nAssorted Bite-Sized Desserts\n Optional Wine Additions:\nGlass of Sparkling Wine or Mimosa – $10\nBottle of Chardonnay\, Rosé\, or Red Blend The Duet\nBottle of Sparkling Rosé – $57.50\nReservations required to ensure a delightful dining experience\nThis is a beautiful way to slow down\, share a meal\, and celebrate the incredible moms in our lives—surrounded by nature\, family\, music\, and award-winning wine. Let’s raise a glass to Mom!\n Celebrate spring\, family\, and friendship at Great Bear Vineyards—because Mom deserves a day as special as she is.
URL:https://visitdavis.org/event/mothers-day-lunch-great-bear-vineyards/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards 24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitdavis.org/wp-content/uploads/b_portwinechocolate-JkHeXb.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
